        <div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first">
    <div id="node-1185094" class="node node-teaser node-type-story"><div class="node-inner">



  

 <a href="/content/fight-good-fight-smokeping" class="imagecache imagecache-teaser imagecache-linked imagecache-teaser_linked"><img src="http://www.linuxjournal.com/files/linuxjournal.com/ufiles/imagecache/teaser/nodeimage/story/11577smokef1.jpg" alt="" title=""  class="imagecache imagecache-teaser" width="100" height="100" /></a> 
  
  


      <h2 class="title">
      <a href="/content/fight-good-fight-smokeping" title="Fight the Good Fight with SmokePing">Fight the Good Fight with SmokePing</a>
    </h2>
  
  

  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
		By <a href="/users/shawn-powers" title="View user profile.">Shawn Powers</a>&nbsp;<!--|
		Nov 11, 2013 -->
     
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"><ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_799 first"><a href="/tag/editors-choice" rel="tag" title="">Editors&#039; Choice</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_256"><a href="/tag/networking" rel="tag" title="">networking</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_21"><a href="/tag/sysadmin" rel="tag" title="">SysAdmin</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_196 last active"><a href="/tag/tech-tips" rel="tag" title="" class="active">Tech Tips</a></li>
</ul></div>
      
  	 </div>
    </div>
  
  
    


  <div class="content">

    
    
            
                    <a href="/content/fight-good-fight-smokeping" class="imagecache imagecache-teaser imagecache-linked imagecache-teaser_linked"></a>        
        

My Internet connection is unstable. I do realize ISPs generally claim
some downtime is expected, and service is not guaranteed, and countless
other excuses are common for intermittent service. I currently pay
$120/month for business-class service, however, and I expect to get
reliable Internet access on a regular basis.<span class="read-more"><a href="/content/fight-good-fight-smokeping"> more>></a></span>
  </div>



  <ul class="links inline"><li class="comment_comments first last"><a href="/content/fight-good-fight-smokeping#comments" title="Jump to the first comment of this posting.">8 comments</a></li>
</ul>
 <!---->




</div></div> <!-- /node-inner, /node -->


