    <div id="node-1163208" class="node node-teaser node-type-story"><div class="node-inner">



  

 <a href="/node/1163208" class="imagecache imagecache-teaser imagecache-linked imagecache-teaser_linked"><img src="http://www.linuxjournal.com/files/linuxjournal.com/ufiles/imagecache/teaser/nodeimage/story/11563androidf1.jpg" alt="" title=""  class="imagecache imagecache-teaser" width="100" height="100" /></a> 
  
  


      <h2 class="title">
      <a href="/node/1163208" title="Dude, Where&#039;s My Car?">Dude, Where&#039;s My Car?</a>
    </h2>
  
  

  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
		By <a href="/users/shawn-powers" title="View user profile.">Shawn Powers</a>&nbsp;<!--|
		Oct 14, 2013 -->
     
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"><ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_192 first"><a href="/tag/android" rel="tag" title="">Android</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_799"><a href="/tag/editors-choice" rel="tag" title="">Editors&#039; Choice</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_328"><a href="/tag/mobile" rel="tag" title="">Mobile</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_196 last active"><a href="/tag/tech-tips" rel="tag" title="" class="active">Tech Tips</a></li>
</ul></div>
      
  	 </div>
    </div>
  
  
    


  <div class="content">

    
    
            
                    <a href="/node/1163208" class="imagecache imagecache-teaser imagecache-linked imagecache-teaser_linked"></a>        
        

<p>
When my family moved to Grand Rapids, Michigan, last year, one of the biggest
adjustments was dealing with city parking. While we usually remember
what side of the mall we parked on, there was a time downtown that I
couldn't remember what parking garage we used, much less what level or
spot.<span class="read-more"><a href="/node/1163208"> more>></a></span></p>
  </div>



  <ul class="links inline"><li class="comment_comments first last"><a href="/node/1163208#comments" title="Jump to the first comment of this posting.">4 comments</a></li>
</ul>
