    <div id="node-1155671" class="node node-teaser node-type-story"><div class="node-inner">



  

 <a href="/content/pitch-perfect-penguins" class="imagecache imagecache-teaser imagecache-linked imagecache-teaser_linked"><img src="http://www.linuxjournal.com/files/linuxjournal.com/ufiles/imagecache/teaser/nodeimage/story/11544mixf1.jpg" alt="" title=""  class="imagecache imagecache-teaser" width="100" height="100" /></a> 
  
  


      <h2 class="title">
      <a href="/content/pitch-perfect-penguins" title="Pitch Perfect Penguins">Pitch Perfect Penguins</a>
    </h2>
  
  

  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
		By <a href="/users/shawn-powers" title="View user profile.">Shawn Powers</a>&nbsp;<!--|
		Sep 26, 2013 -->
     
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"><ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_184 first"><a href="/tag/audio" rel="tag" title="">audio</a></li>
<li class="taxonomy_term_196 last active"><a href="/tag/tech-tips" rel="tag" title="" class="active">Tech Tips</a></li>
</ul></div>
      
  	 </div>
    </div>
  
  
    


  <div class="content">

    
    
            
                    <a href="/content/pitch-perfect-penguins" class="imagecache imagecache-teaser imagecache-linked imagecache-teaser_linked"></a>        
        

<p>
My daughters love the movie Pitch Perfect. I suspect our XBMC has
played it more than 100 times, and I'm not exaggerating. Whether or not you enjoy
young-adult movies about singing competitions and cartoon-like projectile
vomiting, I'll admit it's a pretty fun movie.<span class="read-more"><a href="/content/pitch-perfect-penguins"> more>></a></span></p>
  </div>



