  <div class="content">

    
    
            
                    <a href="/content/non-linux-foss-libnotify-os-x-style" class="imagecache imagecache-teaser imagecache-linked imagecache-teaser_linked"></a>        
        

<p>One of the things I dislike about using Irssi in a terminal window on OS X is that I often miss the screen flash when someone mentions my name in IRC. With some fancy SSH tunneling (maybe more on that some other issue) and a really cool pop-up notification tool, if someone mentions my name, I can't miss it.<span class="read-more"><a href="/content/non-linux-foss-libnotify-os-x-style"> more>></a></span></p>

